name: Lucky Moon
description: Make history with Black Unicorn Black Unicorn is a global holding company specializing in the development of intelligent solutions for the crypto ecosystem. We were born from the union of two entrepreneurs who share the same vision: to build an environment where security, technology, and efficiency connect in a decentralized way. Our purpose is clear, to deliver robust products, based on blockchain, artificial intelligence, and Web3 infrastructure, capable of protecting, enhancing, and generating real value for digital assets. We believe that the future of crypto assets requires more than just decentralization. It requires intelligence, transparency, and security..
